          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-PART-EDITOR-EX.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Part-Editor: Example]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent">Graphic-Area : </text><text styleclass="Body Text">show sketch-elements, dimensions, Part-Axes</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName">Contextual toolbars </text><text styleclass="Body Text">: to the left and right of the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName">Name-tabs </text><text styleclass="Body Text">: the active name tab is the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to which you added the </text><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
        </td>
